  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个零售会员积分系统的状态流转图。核心是从优惠券系统出发，先有个IDLE空闲态，然后能被激活进入FETCH取数状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Retail_CouponSystem",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，IDLE是起点。FETCH之后的数据解析环节，成功和失败要分开处理对吧？比如PARSE状态之后分支到有效和无效两条路？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE",
        "ERROR"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，PARSE解析成功走ARB_READ仲裁读，失败直接进ERROR错误态。另外ERROR最后要能软件清回IDLE。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "PARSE",
        "ARB_READ",
        "ERROR",
        "IDLE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，那我加上ARB_READ获得授权后进入READ读取，然后到ARB_WRITE仲裁写，再授权进入WRITE写入。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARB_READ",
        "READ",
        "ARB_WRITE",
        "WRITE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "WRITE完成后要有个CHAIN链式处理状态，判断是不是最后一条。不是的话返回FETCH继续下一条，是的话进COMPLETE完成态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WRITE",
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "CHAIN到FETCH标\"Next\"，CHAIN到COMPLETE标\"Last\"，这样逻辑清晰。那COMPLETE之后呢？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "CHAIN",
        "FETCH",
        "COMPLETE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "COMPLETE完成后发中断回到IDLE。还有IDLE到FETCH的触发条件叫\"Kick-off\"，FETCH到PARSE是\"Complete\"。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "COMPLETE",
        "IDLE",
        "IDLE",
        "FETCH",
        "FETCH",
        "PARSE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "全部确认了：COMPLETE回IDLE标\"IRQ sent\"，ERROR回IDLE标\"SW clear\"，PARSE到ARB_READ标\"Valid\"，到ERROR标\"Invalid\"。状态机完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
